biography: With a background in physics, Katrin discovered her enthusiasm for data analysis while exploring laser-molecule interactions during her PhD. Hence, she left science to become a consultant at I-WUNDER. Since 2020 she mainly manages projects in the area of data science and software development. Besides, Katrin has a passion for exploring new (project) management techniques and running workshops.
